22    /**
23    * Base bean property handler class, which implements common parts of
24    * reflection-based functionality for accessing a property value
25    * and serializing it.
26    *<p>
27    * Note that current design tries to keep instances immutable (semi-functional
28    * style); mostly because these instances are exposed to application
29    * code and this is to reduce likelihood of data corruption and
30    * synchronization issues.
31    */
